msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Toont de openstaande kunstwerkinzendingen van de ingelogde artiest voor "
"beoordeling en goedkeuring. Plaats dit op je /my-submissions/-pagina of in "
"een Site Editor-template."

